    <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
      <head>Biographical History</head>
      <p>Len Morgan (1894-1957?) was an American novelist during the first-half of the 19th century. Books by the author include



        <emph render="italic">Klondike Adventure</emph> (1940) and



        <emph render="italic">Abilene Trail</emph> (1941).</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
      <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
      <p>The



        <emph render="bold">Len Morgan Manuscripts</emph> consist of two unpublished, undated manuscripts for



        <emph render="italic">Jungle Treasure</emph> and



        <emph render="italic">Lone Star Rangers</emph>.</p>
    </scopecontent>
